1. *Pitala* me da li želim da idem sa njom. (She asked me if I wanted to go with her.)
2. Ona joj je *pitala* da li je sve u redu. (She asked her if everything was okay.)
3. Ja sam *pitala* da li ste vi tu. (I asked if you were here.)
4. Otac je *pitala* zašto je kasnila. (Father asked why she was late.)
5. *Pitala* je njega za njegove planove. (She asked him about his plans.)
6. Njena majka je *pitala* je da li je pronašla posao. (Her mother asked if she found a job.)